282
00:29:33,350 --> 00:29:35,410
If they want to set a death trap,

283
00:29:36,190 --> 00:29:37,730
they'll do it there.

284
00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:39,970
Let's go to the ship

285
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:41,970
to find Heavenly Staff.

286
00:29:50,870 --> 00:29:52,020
Remember.

287
00:29:52,670 --> 00:29:54,100
The patriarch's death trap

288
00:29:54,430 --> 00:29:56,020
must be extremely dangerous.

289
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,380
Act within your capabilities.

290
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:28,970
It seems there used to be a river here.

291
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,479
Only a layer of mud remained

292
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:32,210
after the water receded.

293
00:30:33,350 --> 00:30:35,340
This should be the area
where Sifang City's war

294
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,970
took place.

295
00:30:39,520 --> 00:30:41,589
Why are these jars under all this sand?

296
00:30:41,590 --> 00:30:42,820
Don't touch them.

297
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,930
There's something dangerous

298
00:30:47,830 --> 00:30:49,490
underneath these jars.

299
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:51,349
They must be traps

300
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,669
set by the patriarch.

301
00:30:52,670 --> 00:30:54,580
They're used to resist foreign enemies.

302
00:31:08,150 --> 00:31:09,340
This is rare.

303
00:31:09,870 --> 00:31:11,060
It's the first time

304
00:31:11,350 --> 00:31:13,490
you've listened to anyone but me.

305
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:03,580
Is the patriarch on this ship?

306
00:32:04,280 --> 00:32:05,450
Not necessarily.

307
00:32:05,910 --> 00:32:08,340
He could be anywhere in this area.

308
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:11,060
Let's search the ship first.

309
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:51,349
This ship is so broken

310
00:32:51,350 --> 00:32:53,410
