there's any mechanism.

311
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:36,130
Here.

312
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:41,260
They were the people
who died in Sifang City's war.

313
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:42,970
Were they all killed in battle?

314
00:33:46,520 --> 00:33:48,060
They have no obvious injuries.

315
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:51,890
They looked like
they died from poisoning.

316
00:33:52,670 --> 00:33:54,410
They probably
committed suicide by poisoning.

317
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,580
Something's wrong here.

318
00:33:59,670 --> 00:34:00,890
Let's leave immediately

319
00:34:01,150 --> 00:34:02,300
after finding the staff.

320
00:34:03,320 --> 00:34:04,690
There's something here.

321
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:14,450
Look at these ancient corpses.

322
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:16,700
They should be
the Zhang family's corpses.

323
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:18,220
Their two fingers are very long.

324
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:22,010
They seem to be protecting this thing.

325
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,450
Could the body

326
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:37,780
of the Zhang family's patriarch
be in here?

327
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:41,410
Open it and see.

328
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,660
Whose turn is it?

329
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,220
This needle is poisonous.

330
00:35:34,670 --> 00:35:35,820
It's the mechanism.

331
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,570
We fell into a trap.

332
00:36:12,080 --> 00:36:13,490
Don't move.

333
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:21,050
Look at the saber

334
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:23,780
and the dust on this box.

335
00:36:24,080 --> 00:36:25,439
Something was activated

336
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:27,180
at the bottom of the deck,

337
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,439
causing the entire deck

338
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:30,050
to vibrate at a high frequency

339
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:33,220
and their positions to shift.

340
00:36:35,590 --> 00:36:37,970
There's a defense mechanism
set up by the Zhang family here.

341
00:36:38,270 --> 00:36:40,300
When he cut the sail just now,

342
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,789
all the mechanisms were activated.

343
00:36:42,790 --> 00:36:44,149
That means we'll all die here

344
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:46,050
if we make one wrong move.

345
00:36:46,190 --> 00:36:48,890
The dangers of the Zhang family's traps
are immeasurable,

346
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:51,700
but we can't die here.

347
00:37:17,790 --> 00:37:18,879
I got it.

348
00:37:18,880 --> 00:37:20,340
It's a weight mechanism.

349
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,090
This ship

350
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:23,700
is balanced front to back.

351
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:26,300
Once the mechanism is triggered,

352
00:37:26,750 --> 00:37:29,090
the ship will begin measuring
the weight on the deck.

353
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:31,490
It is difficult

354
00:37:31,630 --> 00:37:33,490
for ordinary people to feel it.

355
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:38,140
Once the deck begins to lose balance,

356
00:37:38,270 --> 00:37:40,010
the defense mechanism will be triggered

357
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:42,450
and the people on board will be killed.

358
00:37:43,790 --> 00:37:45,669
The whole ship is a trap.

359
00:37:45,670 --> 00:37:47,300
Heavenly Staff is certainly not here.

360
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:50,749
Try to keep your balance
and find a chance to get off the ship

361
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:52,340
before searching around the ship.

362
00:37:52,590 --> 00:37:54,260
Keep the ship balanced.

363
00:37:54,710 --> 00:37:56,300
