I have to protect myself.

370
00:38:57,110 --> 00:38:58,260
Zhang Nian.

371
00:38:58,880 --> 00:38:59,860
Don't move.

372
00:39:01,310 --> 00:39:02,490
Get ready to go.

373
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,570
