374
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:07,479
I'll stay alone to save Zhang Nian.

375
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,610
You guys can leave first.

376
00:39:36,670 --> 00:39:37,740
Evacuate!

377
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:00,860
Go.

